@{"??????????????" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(33723,0)"}          33723,0
@{"Level = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(28265,1)"}          28265,x (x= 1-??)
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(29277,255)"}          22977,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


